#: daveden-builderius-enhancements.php:133
msgid "Daveden Builder Enhancements is a companion to Builderius and stays dormant until Builderius is active. Please activate Builderius to use its enhancements."
msgstr ""

#: daveden-builderius-enhancements.php:162
msgid "Daveden Builder Enhancements requires the Builderius plugin. Please install and activate Builderius first, then activate this plugin."
